  "text": [
    "it\u2019s good not to drink",
    "it\u2019s good not to piss",
    "in the sink",
    "it\u2019s good",
    "not to think",
    "the clarion ring",
    "of a glass clinking",
    "with ice good to hear it",
    "fade into a past",
    "you can\u2019t sing",
    "your dumb blues",
    "is over. admit",
    "it was always",
    "borrowed. you paid",
    "no dues you did",
    "no time",
    "but the time spent",
    "sodden. what you thought",
    "I think. your",
    "higher power\u2019s",
    "drunk. god\u2019s",
    "the biggest alky",
    "in the sky",
    "the clouds are whiskey",
    "sours passing by"
  ],
  "title": "Every Day a Shiny Bright New Day",
  "year": ""
}